name: In memory of a game that didn't make it because of lack of time
name_original: In memory of a game that didn't make it because of lack of time
description:
A symbolic game I made in ten minutes in place of the game I was making for the jam. Realized I had only nine hours to pour into  it and also lacked the knowledge to finish it on time, as I didn't have time to work on it before today.

Nevertheless, it was a good experience, and I had the opportunity to learn more. Maybe in a few days I may be able to complete the original project and upload it to another page...

Who knows...
